### Get a task

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.example.org/v3/tasks/[guid]" \
  -X GET \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]"
```

```
Example Response
```

```http
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json

<%= yield_content :single_task %>
```

Retrieve a specific task. The `command` field may be excluded
in the response based on the user's role.

#### Definition
`GET /v3/tasks/:guid`

